Package: wkhtmltopdf
Version: 0.13.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: wkhtmltopdf Team <support@wkhtmltopdf.org>
Homepage: https://wkhtmltopdf.org
Depends: libqt5core5a, libqt5gui5, libqt5network5, libqt5svg5, libqt5xmlpatterns5, libqt5webkit5 | libqt5webenginecore5, libqt5webenginewidgets5, libqt5printsupport5, libssl1.1 | libssl3, libfontconfig1, libfreetype6, libx11-6, libxrender1, libxext6, libc6
Recommends: qtwebengine5-dev, libqt5webenginecore5, libqt5webenginewidgets5
Suggests: xvfb
Description: HTML to PDF converter (with modern CSS support)
 wkhtmltopdf and wkhtmltoimage are command line tools to render HTML into PDF
 and various image formats using Qt rendering engines.
 .
 Version 0.13.0 features:
  * WebEngine backend (Chromium) with full CSS3 support (Flexbox, Grid, Animations)
  * Chromium-based rendering engine for modern web pages
  * Legacy WebKit backend removed
  * Single-backend architecture focused on WebEngine
 .
 This package includes both wkhtmltopdf (HTML to PDF) and wkhtmltoimage
 (HTML to image) converters with the libwkhtmltox shared library.
